createObject.name: createObject
createObject.label: Create an Object
createObject.description: Creates an object based on a selected module (ex: create an account, create a contact, create a ticket ...).

deleteObject.name: deleteObject
deleteObject.label: Delete an Object
deleteObject.description: Deletes a specified object based on id from a selected module (ex: delete an account, delete a contact, delete a ticket ...).

searchObject.name: searchObject
searchObject.label: Search Objects
searchObject.description: Returns multiple objects based on a search criteria from a selected module(ex: accounts where account name contains 'Joe', tickets where subject contains 'Hello', contacts where email contains domain '@gmail.com' ...).

updateObject.name: updateObject
updateObject.label: Update an Object
updateObject.description: Updates a specific object based on id from a selected data (ex: update an account, update a ticket, update a contact ...).

createComment.name: createComment
createComment.label: Add a Comment
createComment.description: Adds a comment to an object based on id for a particular module (tasks, tickets).

editSpamObjects.name: editSpamObjects
editSpamObjects.label: Edit Spam Objects
editSpamObjects.description: Sets or unsets contacts/tickets as spam by specifying their ids into a list.
